ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StudentInterface

    @Component
public class Student
extends Object
implements StudentInterface
    Stores all data relevant to a student.

    Specifically, this data is the student's registration number (ro numar matricol), name, surname, group, grade (ro medie), year of study and optional course preferences. Aside from storing a student's data, this class does nothing.

        Assigns to the created instance, in this order, the registration number, name, surname, group and grade.

        The optional preferences aren't set in the constructor since the preferences may be unknown at the time of importing students.
